WEBVTT

00:01:59.766 --> 00:02:03.430
pata jina, na pakua kumbukumbu zote

00:02:03.430 --> 00:02:07.049
kabla hujasema neno au ongea na mtu

00:02:07.049 --> 00:02:08.425
maana kila mtu anaishia kua

00:02:08.425 --> 00:02:12.026
ameandikwa kabisa na michoro ya
elektroniki.

00:02:12.026 --> 00:02:14.518
Hivyo kuna makampuni kama face.com
ambayo sasa yana

00:02:14.518 --> 00:02:18.252
takribani nyuso bilioni 18 mtandaoni.

00:02:18.252 --> 00:02:19.971
Hichi kilitokea kwenye hii kampuni.

00:02:19.971 --> 00:02:22.554
[Kampuni imeuzwa kwa Facebook, Juni 18, 2012...]

00:02:22.554 --> 00:02:25.207
Kuna makampuni mengine yangeweka kamera

00:02:25.207 --> 00:02:27.630
kama hivi - hii haihusiani na Facebook -

00:02:27.630 --> 00:02:29.962
wanachukua picha yako, na kuilinganisha
mitandaoni

00:02:29.962 --> 00:02:32.069
wanagundua unapenda kuvaa magauni meusi,